transcripts: Exclusively for Bed bath and beyond, the Beekman Duvet cover and bedding collection by Wamsutta offers subtle sophistication and comfort, the beekman duvet cover and pillow shams are 100% cotton matelassé which has a soft texture finish. Coordinating pillow shams have the same diamond matelassé pattern as the duvet cover resulting in a bed that is soft and luxurious the first layer of the bed begins with a soft 100% cotton sheet set in a gray and white pin stripe patter. Euro shams add an ideal backdrop to the bed, crisp white with a contrasting grey trim they are the perfect compliment to the other decorative pillows, the light and airy white cotton royal coverlet and coordinating shams pair beautifully with the duvet color. Decorative pillows add the key fashion elements that complete this elegant bed, the beautiful coordinating pillows accenting this bed suites are an elegant white linen pillow with pleading detail, a soft wooling pillow in charcoal gray, and an ob-longed steel pillow with a nubby texture which adds a nice layer to the bed. The Beekman Duvet cover and bedding collection by Wamsutta is available exclusively online and at select Bed bath and beyond stores.
